'''Sector Alpha''' was a sector in the bizarre space station known as [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']]. Sector Alpha was the central sector of the station and housed, among other important locations, [[The Hub (Zirtran's Anchor)|The Hub]] - the original [[KV-29233-44B|Zirtran barge]] - as well as the gambling den, [[Chabak's]], and the local [[Pandor's Hydrospanner]] repair shop.

The [[Geelan]]s resided primarily in this sector.

